{"tid":1892311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會 : 特首建制鬧不和 證建制實事求是 非盲撐","createTime":"2020-02-22T12:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T16:02:10.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2d242df4e9cdd4c54d6459ad32525a15548d4e36","tid":1892311,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"麥美娟稱會如實向政府反映情況 促團結面對疫情<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道指，特首辦曾撰寫報告，向中央表示特首在疫情中缺乏建制派支持。工聯會立法會議員麥美娟說，不清楚相關文件是否存在，但表示工聯會實事求是，做工會的人坦白直率，會如實向政府反映市民的情況。<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟說，香港防疫工作的困難，很多時候是因為市民受謠傳誤導，希望大家團結冷靜面對疫情，聚焦在防疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於被質疑政府撥款資助口罩商，與有份生產口罩的工聯會涉及利益輸送。麥美娟說，這些言論屬抹黑，自疫情開始已到處尋找口罩派發予市民，亦希望做到本地生產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510182-20200222.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510182-20200222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=1c15366d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510182-20200222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=08c2012c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510182-20200222.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"55ed0cefdbcbdedf6897a4b9a8c9c5f091e9e651","tid":1892311,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"蕭生又中"},{"pid":"4e9b984fc24812fbddfbd27b3b44f13ae26ddd78","tid":1892311,"uid":72581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"收皮喇 想洗底？"},{"pid":"dcd504ee36c9611a47fdd34d80dc611458724b7e","tid":1892311,"uid":41245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"扯貓尾"},{"pid":"8df551f16612ff31272cd14a1fcc74d774ef0dd5","tid":1892311,"uid":146520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"咪又係共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" clas